Package: SYNTHESIS
Type: Package
Title: Structured Yield-Neutral Trust-weighted Heterogeneity-Integrated Statistical Inference System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mahmood Ul", "Hassan", email = "mahmood.hassan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the SYNTHESIS model, a 7-layer meta-analysis methodology for robust evidence synthesis.
    It replaces standard inverse-variance weighting with a multi-layered process of spatial density mapping,
    precision weighting, and quality integration to address systematic bias and noise.
